  "texts": [
    "All the analyses were performed using IBM SPSS Statistics v29.0.",
    "In our study, 18 autopsy sample cases (including 3 COVID-19induced pneumonia cases and 15 non-COVID-19-induced pneumonia cases) coming from unique patients were acquired.",
    "This sample size was on par with prior research on similar topics and confirmed to be sufficient by collaborating pathologists.",
    "No data were excluded from the analysis.",
    "Among 18 cases, 3 cases corresponding to COVID-19induced pneumonia were randomly selected by a board-certified pathologist, and 15 cases corresponding to non-COVID-19-induced pneumonia were randomly selected by another board-certified pathologist."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}